<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Email Template</title>
  <style>
    .container {
      width: 55%;
      height: auto;
      border: 3px solid black;
      position: absolute;
      top: 70%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #594FF5;
      width: 100%;
      border-bottom: 3px solid black;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .header img {
      height: 52px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .content p:first-child {
      font-size: 25px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .content p:nth-child(2) {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .call-to-action {
      position: relative;
    }

    .call-to-action .overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 5px;
      left: 5px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background-color: black;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .call-to-action .button {
      width: 170px;
      border: 3px solid black;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      background-color: #ffc34d;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .footer {
      border-top: 3px solid black;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #d9d9d9;
    }

    .footer .social-icons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .footer img {
      height: 20px;
      border: 2px solid black;
      margin: 0 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="logo.png" alt="Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi, [first name]!</p>
      <p>Thank you for creating an account on the<br>London Filmed booking platform.</p>
      <p>Your account manager is [first name surname].</p>
      <p>If there is anything you need with, you can<br>get in touch with them at [email address]</p>
      <p>Or, feel free to</p>
      <div class="call-to-action">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="button">Book a call</div>
      </div>
      <p>If you're ready to get started</p>
      <p>create a quote for your next event</p>
      <p>Thanks,</p>
      <p>London Filmed</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social-icons">
        <img src="linkedIcon.png" alt="LinkedIn">
        <img src="instagramIcon.png" alt="Instagram">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>